47A4002A.Line31.710B6: Our victory is prophesied in the Heavens.

6F205668.Line11.710B6: Yet you stand before me unscathed. I know his ways. That is approval enough for me.

F556A4CB.Line23.710B6: In the name of the Light, I bless you. May the Light flow through you and keep you from corruption and sin.
